  "original_title": "10\u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 10%    \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Only 10% of buses will run till the 10th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gemunu Wijeratne, president of the All Ceylon Private Bus Owners' Association, said only 10 percent of private buses would be in service until July 10.",
        "He made the remarks while addressing a media briefing in Colombo today (29).",
        "He also said that buses were forced to run once in two days due to fuel shortages.",
        "Meanwhile, the National Transport Commission (NTC) today (29) submitted a recommendation to revise bus fares, with bus owners demanding a 30 per cent increase in bus fares and a minimum fare increase of 40 rupees from Friday, July 1."
      ],
